---
---
<section id="formats" class="py-16 border-b border-border">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
    <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1 font-sans">4. File Formats</h2>
    <p class="text-fg-dim text-xs mb-8">Simple frontmatter + markdown for content. Plain JSON for config. No YAML dependency.</p>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <!-- Skill -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">skills/code-review/skill.md</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code><span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">id</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">code-review</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">name</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">Code Review Expert</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">description</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">Thorough code review</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">enabled</span>: <span class="text-accent-blue">true</span>
<span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>

<span class="text-fg">Review code changes for:</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">- Security vulnerabilities</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">- Performance implications</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">- Test coverage gaps</span></code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Memory -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">memories/arch-decisions.md</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code><span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">id</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">arch_001</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">title</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">Database Architecture</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">content</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">PostgreSQL with Drizzle ORM</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">importance</span>: <span class="text-accent-blue">high</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">tags</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">database, architecture, orm</span>
<span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>

<span class="text-fg">We chose PostgreSQL over MongoDB for</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">relational data integrity and complex</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">query support across billing.</span></code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- MCP -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">mcp.json</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code>&#123;
  <span class="text-accent-cyan">"mcpServers"</span>: &#123;
    <span class="text-accent-amber">"filesystem"</span>: &#123;
      <span class="text-accent-cyan">"command"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"npx"</span>,
      <span class="text-accent-cyan">"args"</span>: [<span class="text-accent-amber">"@mcp/server-filesystem"</span>],
      <span class="text-accent-cyan">"transport"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"stdio"</span>
    &#125;,
    <span class="text-accent-amber">"github"</span>: &#123;
      <span class="text-accent-cyan">"url"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"https://api.github.com/mcp"</span>,
      <span class="text-accent-cyan">"transport"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"streamable-http"</span>
    &#125;
  &#125;
&#125;</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- agents.md -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">agents.md</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code><span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">kind</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">agents</span>
<span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>

<span class="text-fg"># Project Guidelines</span>

<span class="text-fg-muted">## Build &amp; Test</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">- Use `pnpm` for package management</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">- Run `pnpm test` before committing</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">- TypeScript strict mode required</span></code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Sub-Agent profile -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">agents/code-reviewer/agent.md</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code><span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">id</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">code-reviewer</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">name</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">Code Reviewer</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">description</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">Reviews code for security</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">role</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">delegation-target</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">enabled</span>: <span class="text-accent-blue">true</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">connection-type</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">internal</span>
<span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>

<span class="text-fg">You are a code review specialist.</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">Focus on security vulnerabilities,</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">performance, and test coverage.</span></code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Sub-Agent config.json -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">agents/code-reviewer/config.json</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code>&#123;
  <span class="text-accent-cyan">"toolConfig"</span>: &#123;
    <span class="text-accent-cyan">"disabledServers"</span>: [<span class="text-accent-amber">"filesystem"</span>],
    <span class="text-accent-cyan">"enabledBuiltinTools"</span>: [<span class="text-accent-amber">"mark_work_complete"</span>]
  &#125;,
  <span class="text-accent-cyan">"modelConfig"</span>: &#123;
    <span class="text-accent-cyan">"mcpToolsProviderId"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"openai"</span>,
    <span class="text-accent-cyan">"mcpToolsOpenaiModel"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"gpt-4o"</span>
  &#125;,
  <span class="text-accent-cyan">"connection"</span>: &#123;
    <span class="text-accent-cyan">"type"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"stdio"</span>,
    <span class="text-accent-cyan">"command"</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">"my-agent"</span>,
    <span class="text-accent-cyan">"args"</span>: [<span class="text-accent-amber">"--mode"</span>, <span class="text-accent-amber">"review"</span>]
  &#125;
&#125;</code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Knowledge Note -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">knowledge/discord/recaps/recap-2026-03-18/recap-2026-03-18.md</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code><span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">kind</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">note</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">id</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">discord-recap-2026-03-18</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">title</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">Discord recap for Mar 18</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">context</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">search-only</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">updatedAt</span>: <span class="text-accent-blue">1770000000000</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">tags</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">discord, recap</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">group</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">discord</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">series</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">recaps</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">entryType</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">entry</span>
<span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>

<span class="text-fg">Key discussion topics from today's</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">Discord channels including protocol</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">updates and community feedback.</span></code></pre>
      </div>

      <!-- Repeat Task -->
      <div class="code-block rounded-md overflow-hidden">
        <div class="px-4 py-2 border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs">tasks/daily-code-review/task.md</div>
        <pre class="p-4 text-[13px] leading-relaxed overflow-x-auto"><code><span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">kind</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">task</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">id</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">daily-code-review</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">name</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">Daily Code Review</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">intervalMinutes</span>: <span class="text-accent-blue">60</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">enabled</span>: <span class="text-accent-blue">true</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">runOnStartup</span>: <span class="text-accent-blue">false</span>
<span class="text-accent-cyan">profileId</span>: <span class="text-accent-amber">abc-123</span>
<span class="text-fg-dim">---</span>

<span class="text-fg">Review all open pull requests and</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">summarize their status. Check for</span>
<span class="text-fg-muted">any failing CI pipelines.</span></code></pre>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Frontmatter note -->
    <div class="mt-6 spec-card rounded-md p-4 text-xs text-fg-muted leading-relaxed">
      <span class="text-fg">Frontmatter format:</span> Uses <code class="text-accent-cyan">---</code> fences with simple <code class="text-accent-cyan">key: value</code> lines.
      Not full YAML — no external dependencies. Values can be quoted. List fields accept CSV (<code class="text-accent-cyan">tags: a, b, c</code>)
      or JSON arrays (<code class="text-accent-cyan">tags: ["a", "b"]</code>). Keys are sorted deterministically for clean diffs.
    </div>

    <!-- Knowledge note fields -->
    <div class="mt-4 spec-card rounded-md p-4 text-xs text-fg-muted leading-relaxed">
      <span class="text-fg">Knowledge note fields:</span> Notes support optional grouping metadata.
      <table class="w-full mt-3 text-[13px]">
        <thead>
          <tr class="border-b border-border text-fg-dim text-xs text-left">
            <th class="py-1.5 pr-4 font-normal">Field</th>
            <th class="py-1.5 pr-4 font-normal">Type</th>
            <th class="py-1.5 font-normal">Description</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody class="text-fg-muted">
          <tr class="border-b border-border-light">
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4"><code class="text-accent-cyan">group</code></td>
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4">string</td>
            <td class="py-1.5">Top-level grouping (e.g. <code class="text-fg-dim">discord</code>, <code class="text-fg-dim">docs</code>)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-border-light">
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4"><code class="text-accent-cyan">series</code></td>
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4">string</td>
            <td class="py-1.5">Sub-grouping within a group (e.g. <code class="text-fg-dim">recaps</code>, <code class="text-fg-dim">changelogs</code>)</td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="border-b border-border-light">
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4"><code class="text-accent-cyan">entryType</code></td>
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4"><code class="text-fg-dim">note</code> | <code class="text-fg-dim">entry</code> | <code class="text-fg-dim">overview</code></td>
            <td class="py-1.5">
              <code class="text-fg-dim">note</code> — standalone note;
              <code class="text-fg-dim">entry</code> — item in a series;
              <code class="text-fg-dim">overview</code> — summary/index (e.g. current-state)
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr>
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4"><code class="text-accent-cyan">context</code></td>
            <td class="py-1.5 pr-4">string</td>
            <td class="py-1.5"><code class="text-fg-dim">search-only</code> — available via search; <code class="text-fg-dim">prompt</code> — injected into context</td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p class="mt-3">
        <span class="text-fg">Folder layouts:</span>
        Flat — <code class="text-accent-cyan">knowledge/&lt;slug&gt;/&lt;slug&gt;.md</code> ·
        Grouped — <code class="text-accent-cyan">knowledge/&lt;group&gt;/&lt;series&gt;/&lt;slug&gt;/&lt;slug&gt;.md</code>
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

